OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1775678753
OL,3,CDissident republican Easter parade
OL,4,Cheld in Derry
OL,6,FA dissident republican parade has
OL,7,Ftaken place in Londonderry.
OL,9,FThe annual Easter Monday parade in
OL,10,FDerry marks the Easter Rising against
OL,11,FBritish rule in Dublin in 1916.
OL,13,FThe parade started in the Central
OL,14,FDrive area of Creggan before making
OL,15,Fits way to the City Cemetery.
OL,17,FA police helicopter monitored the
OL,18,Fprocession overhead but there was no
OL,19,Fvisible police presence on the ground.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/5
