OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1775678753
OL,3,CDissident republican Easter parade
OL,4,Cheld in Derry
OL,6,FThere was a colour party of people
OL,7,Fwearing face coverings, sunglasses and
OL,8,Fparamilitary-style dress, carrying the
OL,9,FIrish flag and republican flags.
OL,11,FA crowd of a couple of hundred people
OL,12,Ffollowed the parade to the cemetery,
OL,13,Fincluding a number of young people
OL,14,Fwith their faces covered, some
OL,15,Fcarrying petrol bombs and planks of
OL,16,Fwood.
OL,18,FThe event, billed as the "Unfinished
OL,19,FRevolution National Easter
OL,20,FCommemoration", concluded with
OL,21,Fspeeches at the cemetery.
OL,26,@zD@ZOU|D@NO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/5
