PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1775678753
OL,3,CDissident republican Easter parade
OL,4,Cheld in Derry
OL,6,FA small fire was started in the middle
OL,7,Fof the road outside some shops in the
OL,8,FCreggan area.
OL,10,FThe dissident republican event has
OL,11,Fsparked scenes of violence in previous
OL,12,Fyears.
OL,14,FThe organisers of the parade ` the
OL,15,FNational Republican Commemoration
OL,16,FCommittee ` had applied to the Parades
OL,17,FCommission for permission for the
OL,18,FEaster Monday event.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/5
